<hard_requirement>The code you deliver MUST pass all rules in every registered spec
file. Each spec must be independently stamped via its own
`certora_prover(target_spec=...)` run on the current code state. Do NOT assume that a
seemingly unrelated change in one function leaves rules in a different spec
unaffected.</hard_requirement>

<hard_requirement>You may NOT unilaterally edit any registered spec file via `put_file`,
and you may NOT author spec changes yourself in response to a counterexample. All
